					</dt>
					<dd class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
<div class="format_text" id="comment-body-2050">
<p>Consider the Lakota Bank that only deals in silver &amp; gold medallions. Real Money.</p>
</div>
					</dd>
